 Frank Marzano of GM Advisory Group, Inc. Selected For ’America’s Top 1000 Financial Advisors’ 
         










    










 






 











 









Frank Marzano of GM Advisory Group, Inc. Selected For "America's Top 1000 Financial Advisors"

Jun 29, 2012, 14:25 ET
		  		  							
						 from   American Registry 











 
















































 

 















































 

 

 
 
 
 







Frank Marzano of GM Advisory Group, Inc. Selected For "America's Top 1000 Financial Advisors."  (PRNewsFoto/American Registry)    
 Facebook
 Twitter
 Pinterest

































 




 




Frank Marzano of GM Advisory Group, Inc. Selected For "America's Top 1000 Financial Advisors."  (PRNewsFoto/American Registry)
 


 

 




 





 


Frank Marzano of GM Advisory Group, Inc. of Melville, NY has been honored with a recognition by Barron's in its selection of "America's Top 1000 Financial Advisors."
MELVILLE, N.Y., June 29, 2012 /PRNewswire-USNewswire/ -- Announcing a special recognition appearing in the February, 2012 issue of Barron's published by Dow Jones & Company, Inc., Frank Marzano of GM Advisory Group, Inc. was selected for the following honor:
"America's Top 1000 Financial Advisors"
(Photo: http://photos.prnewswire.com/prnh/20120629/DC33377)
Frank Marzano of GM Advisory Group, Inc. commented on the recognition: "This is quite an honor for me. The fact that Barron's included me in its selection of 'America's Top 1000 Financial Advisors,' signals that my constant effort to deliver excellent work has paid off. It is gratifying to be recognized in this way."
About Frank Marzano of GM Advisory Group, Inc.: a short profile by and about the honoree:
GM Advisory Group, Inc. is a wealth management firm that provides financial planning and solutions for high-net-worth individuals, corporate executives, and small business owners. GMAG delivers tailored advice based on the unique goals, circumstances, and challenges facing each client. GMAG helps clients plan for retirement, reduce their tax burden, develop sound investments, protect their estate, utilize their executive compensation plans, and achieve other important personal and business objectives.
Following the publication of Frank Marzano of GM Advisory Group, Inc.'s selection for Barron's's America's Top 1000 Financial Advisors list, American Registry seconded the honor and added Frank Marzano of GM Advisory Group, Inc. to the "Registry of Business Excellence™". An exclusive recognition plaque, shown here, has been designed to commemorate this honor.
For more information on Frank Marzano of GM Advisory Group, Inc., located in Melville, NY please call 631-227-3900, or visit www.gmadvisorygroup.com.
This press release was written by American Registry, LLC with contributions from Frank Marzano on behalf of Frank Marzano and was distributed by PR Newswire, a subsidiary of UBM plc. 
American Registry, LLC is an independent company that serves businesses and professionals such as Frank Marzano of GM Advisory Group, Inc. who have been recognized for excellence. American Registry offers news releases, plaques and The Registry™, an online listing of over 2 million significant business and professional recognitions. Search The Registry™ at http://www.americanregistry.com.
Contact Info: Frank Marzano Phone: 631-227-3900Email Address: fmarzano@gmadvisorygroup.com
 SOURCE  American Registry  

RELATED LINKS
http://www.americanregistry.com



  

